                <figure>
                    <graphic n="1005" width="11.866877777777777cm" height="7.874cm" url="/tmp/tmpctcydl59/Pictures/d8464f79d68062a6160f98a40815a508.png" rend="inline"/>
                </figure>
                <p style="text-align: left; text-align: center;">
                    <hi rend="bold" style="font-size:10pt">Figure 5.</hi>
                    <hi style="font-size:10pt" xml:space="preserve"> Evolution of accuracy (character and word accuracy) across steps. Step 0 represents the testing of CATMuS-medieval without fine-tuning.</hi>
                </p>
                <figure>
                    <graphic n="1006" width="13.838552777777778cm" height="12.820277777777777cm" url="/tmp/tmpctcydl59/Pictures/d8464f79d68062a6160f98a40815a508.png" rend="inline"/>
